{"data":{"metadata":{"authors":{},"created_at":1645838554000,"identifier":"/docs/themeing/custom-properties","modified_at":1645838554000,"sections":[{"identifier":"custom-properties","level":1,"text":"Custom Properties"},{"identifier":"via-style","level":2,"text":"Via Style"},{"identifier":"via-classes","level":2,"text":"Via Classes"},{"identifier":"via-global-stylesheet","level":2,"text":"Via Global Stylesheet"}],"snippets":[{"identifier":"custom-properties-style","script":"<script>\n    import {Button} from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Button style=\"--button-padding-y:5;\">\n    I was customized via style!\n</Button>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Custom Properties Style"},{"identifier":"custom-properties-css","script":"<script>\n    import {Button} from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Button class=\"custom-properties-class\">\n    I was customized via a class!\n</Button>\n\n<style>\n    :global(.custom-properties-class) {\n        --button-padding-y: 5;\n    }\n</style>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Custom Properties CSS"},{"identifier":"custom-properties-global-stylesheet","script":"<html>\n    <head>\n        <link\n            rel=\"stylesheet\"\n            href=\"/path/to/kahi-ui.framework.css\"\n        />\n\n        <link\n            rel=\"stylesheet\"\n            href=\"/path/to/kahi-ui.theme.default.css\"\n        />\n\n        <style>\n            :root {\n                --button-padding-y: 5;\n            }\n        </style>\n    </head>\n\n    <body>\n        ...\n    </body>\n</html>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Custom Properties Global Stylesheet"}],"title":"Custom Properties"},"text":"Custom Properties WARNING : All CSS Custom Properties are considered unstable and subject to change before v1.0. In supporting Components and for the global theme, you can use CSS Custom Properties to alter the look and feel of the Framework. Via Style You can customize the Custom Properties via inline styles as shown below. <script> import {Button} from \"@kahi-ui/framework\"; </script> <Button style=\"--button-padding-y:5;\"> I was customized via style! </Button> Via Classes You can also use CSS classes to customize them as well. <script> import {Button} from \"@kahi-ui/framework\"; </script> <Button class=\"custom-properties-class\"> I was customized via a class! </Button> <style> :global(.custom-properties-class) { --button-padding-y: 5; } </style> Via Global Stylesheet IMPORTANT : Make sure to declare your customized Custom Properties after you have loaded the Framework + Theme stylesheets. Otherwise they will be ignored. You can finally use global stylesheets to keep all your customizations in one spot. <!-- prettier-ignore --> <html> <head> <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/path/to/kahi-ui.framework.css\" /> <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/path/to/kahi-ui.theme.default.css\" /> <style> :root { --button-padding-y: 5; } </style> </head> <body> ... </body> </html> ","references":{"custom_properties":{},"events":{},"properties":{},"slots":{}},"render":"<blockquote data-palette=\"alert\">\n<p><strong>WARNING</strong>: All CSS Custom Properties are considered unstable and subject to change before <code>v1.0</code>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>In <a href=\"../interactables/button#api-reference\" svelte:prefetch=\"true\">supporting Components</a> and for the global theme, you can use <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/--*\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">CSS Custom Properties</a> to alter the look and feel of the Framework.</p>\n<h2 id=\"via-style\">Via Style</h2>\n<p>You can customize the Custom Properties via inline styles as shown below.</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight language-svelte\" data-identifier=\"custom-properties-style\" data-mode=\"repl\" data-syntax=\"svelte\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>Button<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@kahi-ui/framework\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>--button-padding-y:5;<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    I was customized via style!\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre><h2 id=\"via-classes\">Via Classes</h2>\n<p>You can also use CSS classes to customize them as well.</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight language-svelte\" data-identifier=\"custom-properties-css\" data-mode=\"repl\" data-syntax=\"svelte\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>Button<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@kahi-ui/framework\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>custom-properties-class<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    I was customized via a class!\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n    <span class=\"token selector\">:global(.custom-properties-class)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">--button-padding-y</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre><h2 id=\"via-global-stylesheet\">Via Global Stylesheet</h2>\n<blockquote data-palette=\"negative\">\n<p><strong>IMPORTANT</strong>: Make sure to declare your customized Custom Properties after you have loaded the Framework + Theme stylesheets. Otherwise they will be ignored.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>You can finally use global stylesheets to keep all your customizations in one spot.</p>\n<!-- prettier-ignore -->\n<pre class=\"highlight language-svelte\" data-identifier=\"custom-properties-global-stylesheet\" data-mode=\"default\" data-syntax=\"svelte\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span>\n            <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n            <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>/path/to/kahi-ui.framework.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span>\n            <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n            <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>/path/to/kahi-ui.theme.default.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n            <span class=\"token selector\">:root</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                <span class=\"token property\">--button-padding-y</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        ...\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre>"}}